        //    (ICheckoutCheatModeExtension)ActivatorUtilities.CreateInstance(provider, typeof(ZanoCheckoutCheatModeExtension), new object[] { fusdNetwork, fusdPmi }));

        services.AddUIExtension("server-nav", "/Views/Zano/ServerNavZanoExtension.cshtml");
        services.AddUIExtension("store-nav", "/Views/Zano/StoreNavZanoExtension.cshtml");
        services.AddUIExtension("store-wallets-nav", "/Views/Zano/StoreWalletsNavZanoExtension.cshtml");
        services.AddUIExtension("store-invoices-payments", "/Views/Zano/ViewZanoLikePaymentData.cshtml");
        services.AddUIExtension("checkout-end", "/Views/Zano/CheckoutHeaderZanoFixedAmount.cshtml");
        services.AddSingleton<ISyncSummaryProvider, ZanoSyncSummaryProvider>();
    }
    class SimpleTransactionLinkProvider : DefaultTransactionLinkProvider
    {
        public SimpleTransactionLinkProvider(string blockExplorerLink) : base(blockExplorerLink)
        {
        }

        public override string GetTransactionLink(string paymentId)
        {
            if (string.IsNullOrEmpty(BlockExplorerLink))
            {
                return null;
            }
            return string.Format(CultureInfo.InvariantCulture, BlockExplorerLink, paymentId);
        }
    }

    private static ZanoLikeConfiguration ConfigureZanoLikeConfiguration(IServiceProvider serviceProvider)
    {
        var configuration = serviceProvider.GetService<IConfiguration>();
        var btcPayNetworkProvider = serviceProvider.GetService<BTCPayNetworkProvider>();
        var result = new ZanoLikeConfiguration();
        var settingsRepository = serviceProvider.GetService<ISettingsRepository>();
        Controllers.ZanoServerSettings saved = null;
        try
        {
            saved = settingsRepository?.GetSettingAsync<Controllers.ZanoServerSettings>("ZanoServerSettings")?.GetAwaiter().GetResult();
        }
        catch { }

        var supportedNetworks = btcPayNetworkProvider.GetAll()
            .OfType<ZanoLikeSpecificBtcPayNetwork>();

        foreach (var zanoLikeSpecificBtcPayNetwork in supportedNetworks)
        {
            var daemonUri =
                configuration.GetOrDefault<Uri>($"{zanoLikeSpecificBtcPayNetwork.CryptoCode}_daemon_uri",
                    null);
            var walletDaemonUri =
                configuration.GetOrDefault<Uri>(
                    $"{zanoLikeSpecificBtcPayNetwork.CryptoCode}_wallet_daemon_uri", null);
            var cashCowWalletDaemonUri =
                configuration.GetOrDefault<Uri>(
                    $"{zanoLikeSpecificBtcPayNetwork.CryptoCode}_cashcow_wallet_daemon_uri", null);
            var walletDaemonWalletDirectory =
                configuration.GetOrDefault<string>(
                    $"{zanoLikeSpecificBtcPayNetwork.CryptoCode}_wallet_daemon_walletdir", null);
            var daemonUsername =
                configuration.GetOrDefault<string>(
                    $"{zanoLikeSpecificBtcPayNetwork.CryptoCode}_daemon_username", null);
            var daemonPassword =
                configuration.GetOrDefault<string>(
                    $"{zanoLikeSpecificBtcPayNetwork.CryptoCode}_daemon_password", null);

            // Override from saved server settings when present
            if (saved is not null)
            {
                if (string.Equals(zanoLikeSpecificBtcPayNetwork.CryptoCode, "ZANO", StringComparison.InvariantCultureIgnoreCase))
                {
                    daemonUri ??= saved.ZANO_DAEMON_URI;
                    walletDaemonUri ??= saved.ZANO_WALLET_DAEMON_URI;
                    daemonUsername ??= saved.ZANO_DAEMON_USERNAME;
                    daemonPassword ??= saved.ZANO_DAEMON_PASSWORD;
                    walletDaemonWalletDirectory ??= saved.WALLET_DIR;
                }
                //else if (string.Equals(zanoLikeSpecificBtcPayNetwork.CryptoCode, "FUSD", StringComparison.InvariantCultureIgnoreCase))
                //{
                //    daemonUri ??= saved.FUSD_DAEMON_URI;
                //    walletDaemonUri ??= saved.FUSD_WALLET_DAEMON_URI;
                //    daemonUsername ??= saved.FUSD_DAEMON_USERNAME;
                //    daemonPassword ??= saved.FUSD_DAEMON_PASSWORD;
                //    walletDaemonWalletDirectory ??= saved.WALLET_DIR;
                //}
            }
            if (daemonUri == null || walletDaemonUri == null)
            {
                var logger = serviceProvider.GetRequiredService<ILogger<ZanoPlugin>>();
                var cryptoCode = zanoLikeSpecificBtcPayNetwork.CryptoCode.ToUpperInvariant();
                if (daemonUri is null)
                {
                    logger.LogWarning($"BTCPAY_{cryptoCode}_DAEMON_URI is not configured");
                }
                if (walletDaemonUri is null)
                {
                    logger.LogWarning($"BTCPAY_{cryptoCode}_WALLET_DAEMON_URI is not configured");
                }
                logger.LogWarning($"{cryptoCode} got disabled as it is not fully configured.");
            }
            else
            {
                result.ZanoLikeConfigurationItems.Add(zanoLikeSpecificBtcPayNetwork.CryptoCode, new ZanoLikeConfigurationItem()
                {
                    DaemonRpcUri = daemonUri,
                    Username = daemonUsername,
                    Password = daemonPassword,
                    InternalWalletRpcUri = walletDaemonUri,
                    WalletDirectory = walletDaemonWalletDirectory,
                    CashCowWalletRpcUri = cashCowWalletDaemonUri,
                });
            }
        }

        // Add FUSD configuration if not already present
        //if (!result.ZanoLikeConfigurationItems.ContainsKey("FUSD"))
        //{
        //    // Reuse ZANO settings for FUSD by default
        //    var fusdDaemonUri = configuration.GetOrDefault<Uri>("FUSD_daemon_uri", null) ?? configuration.GetOrDefault<Uri>("ZANO_daemon_uri", null);
        //    var fusdWalletDaemonUri = configuration.GetOrDefault<Uri>("FUSD_wallet_daemon_uri", null) ?? configuration.GetOrDefault<Uri>("ZANO_wallet_daemon_uri", null);
        //    var fusdCashCowWalletDaemonUri = configuration.GetOrDefault<Uri>("FUSD_cashcow_wallet_daemon_uri", null);
        //    var fusdWalletDaemonWalletDirectory = configuration.GetOrDefault<string>("FUSD_wallet_daemon_walletdir", null);
        //    var fusdDaemonUsername = configuration.GetOrDefault<string>("FUSD_daemon_username", null) ?? configuration.GetOrDefault<string>("ZANO_daemon_username", null);
        //    var fusdDaemonPassword = configuration.GetOrDefault<string>("FUSD_daemon_password", null) ?? configuration.GetOrDefault<string>("ZANO_daemon_password", null);

        //    if (saved is not null)
        //    {
        //        fusdDaemonUri ??= saved.ZANO_DAEMON_URI;
        //        fusdWalletDaemonUri ??= saved.ZANO_WALLET_DAEMON_URI;
        //        fusdDaemonUsername ??= saved.ZANO_DAEMON_USERNAME;
        //        fusdDaemonPassword ??= saved.ZANO_DAEMON_PASSWORD;
        //        fusdWalletDaemonWalletDirectory ??= saved.WALLET_DIR;
        //    }

        //    if (fusdDaemonUri != null && fusdWalletDaemonUri != null)
        //    {
        //        result.ZanoLikeConfigurationItems.Add("FUSD", new ZanoLikeConfigurationItem()
        //        {
        //            DaemonRpcUri = fusdDaemonUri,
        //            Username = fusdDaemonUsername,
        //            Password = fusdDaemonPassword,
        //            InternalWalletRpcUri = fusdWalletDaemonUri,
        //            WalletDirectory = fusdWalletDaemonWalletDirectory,
        //            CashCowWalletRpcUri = fusdCashCowWalletDaemonUri,
        //        });
        //    }
        //}
        return result;
    }
